<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Rational Software.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Rational Software.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- SoundView Financial Groups Inc said analyst Kris Tuttle downgraded Rational Software Corp to hold from buy.</p>
<p>-- Soundview said the long-term rating remains as buy.</p>
<p>-- Rational Software said Monday it agreed to acquire Pure Atria Corp.</p>
<p>-- Rational Software, which develops, markets, and supports a comprehensive solution that automates the component-based development of software, lost 6-7/8 to 16-1/2.</p>
</text>
